<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Registrasi Warga - <%= settings.nama_desa || 'Desa Ujunggebang' %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css">
</head>
<body>

  <div class="auth-container" style="padding: 40px 24px;">
    <div class="auth-card" style="max-width: 520px; padding: 40px;">
      <div class="auth-header" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <a href="/" class="auth-logo">U</a>
        <h2>Registrasi Akun Warga</h2>
        <p>Hubungkan NIK KTP Anda ke Sistem Layanan Online</p>
      </div>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-danger">
          <span>⚠️</span>
          <div style="font-size: 13px;"><%= error %></div>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <div style="background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.5;">
        <strong>💡 Petunjuk Pendaftaran:</strong>
        <p style="margin-top: 4px;">Pendaftaran hanya dapat disetujui jika NIK Anda sudah terdaftar di basis data penduduk Kantor Desa Ujunggebang. Ketik Nama Lengkap Anda <strong>persis seperti di KTP</strong>.</p>
      </div>

      <form action="/register" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="nik">NOMOR INDUK KEPENDUDUKAN (NIK)</label>
          <input type="text" id="nik" name="nik" class="form-control" placeholder="16 Digit NIK KTP Anda" maxlength="16" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="nama">NAMA LENGKAP (Sesuai KTP)</label>
          <input type="text" id="nama" name="nama" class="form-control" placeholder="Nama Lengkap Anda" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="no_hp">NOMOR HP / WHATSAPP</label>
          <input type="text" id="no_hp" name="no_hp" class="form-control" placeholder="Contoh: 62812xxxxxxx atau 0812xxxxxxx" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="password">PASSWORD</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Min. 6 Karakter" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="confirm_password">KONFIRMASI PASSWORD</label>
            <input type="password" id="confirm_password" name="confirm_password" class="form-control" placeholder="Ulangi Password" required>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn-sm btn-sm-primary" style="width: 100%; padding: 14px; font-size: 15px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); margin-top: 10px;">
          Daftarkan Akun Baru
        </button>
      </form>

      <div class="auth-footer">
        <p>Sudah memiliki akun? <a href="/login">Login di sini &rarr;</a></p>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 11px;"><a href="/" style="color: var(--text-light); font-weight: 500;">&larr; Kembali ke Website Desa</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
